channel.title: Changing IP in 562 Mezzyscape
channel.description:
Hi. I have looked at a lot of tutorials on how to change the 562 client ip but none are working. Client.java seems to not have a spot for a ip. I have a mezzyscape 562 client.
Once again, how do you change the IP of a mezzyscape 562 client.
